OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1782562704
OL,3,CTeenager charged with murder after
OL,4,Cbody found in search for missing girl
OL,6,FA 14-year-old boy has been charged
OL,7,Fwith murder after a female body was
OL,8,Ffound in a park in Blaina, near Ebbw
OL,9,FVale, late on Monday 22 June.
OL,11,FThe teenager from the Blaenau Gwent
OL,12,Farea, who cannot be named for legal
OL,13,Freasons, was remanded in police
OL,14,Fcustody to appear before Newport
OL,15,FMagistrates Court on Friday, 26 June.
OL,17,FGwent police have confirmed the white
OL,18,FBritish boy was arrested after the
OL,19,Fbody of a female was found in the
OL,20,FDuffryn Park area of Blaina at around
OL,21,F10pm on Monday, 22 June.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/5
