PN,43402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1782562704
OL,3,CTeenager charged with murder after
OL,4,Cbody found in search for missing girl
OL,6,FThe body has not yet been formally
OL,7,Fidentified, but the family of a
OL,8,Fmissing 14-year-old girl, named only
OL,9,Fas Lilly, has been informed.
OL,11,FShe had been reported missing having
OL,12,Flast been seen in High Street, Blaina,
OL,13,Fat around 6.50pm on Saturday, 20 June.
OL,15,FParts of Pilgrims Park, which is
OL,16,Fadjacent to the A467 in Blaina, were
OL,17,Fcordoned off after the body was
OL,18,Fdiscovered.
OL,20,FFloral tributes were left close to the
OL,21,Fscene by members of the public.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/5
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
