FL,435,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1782562704
OL,3,CTeenager charged with murder after
OL,4,Cbody found in search for missing girl
OL,6,FDetective Chief Inspector Steven
OL,7,FThomas said: "Our thoughts are with
OL,8,Fthe family and friends of (the victim)
OL,9,Fat this difficult time.
OL,11,F"We understand that there has been a
OL,12,Fgreat deal of interest in this ongoing
OL,13,Finvestigation. It is vital that people
OL,14,Fconsider how their language,
OL,15,Fespecially comments made online, could
OL,16,Faffect our ability to bring anyone
OL,17,Ffound to have committed a criminal
OL,18,Foffence to justice."
OL,26,@pD@[pmpD@fpnsD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/5
