FL,435,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1782562704
OL,3,CTeenager charged with murder after
OL,4,Cbody found in search for missing girl
OL,6,FHe confirmed significant developments
OL,7,Fhad been made during the
OL,8,Finvestigation, however enquiries are
OL,9,Fongoing and an increased police
OL,10,Fpresence will be in force in the area.
OL,12,FHe continued: "Examinations of scenes
OL,13,Fwill be continuing over the coming
OL,14,Fdays, including at Duffryn Park, where
OL,15,Fcordons remain in place.
OL,17,F"I would like to thank local residents
OL,18,Ffor their continued support and those
OL,19,Fimpacted by the cordons for their
OL,20,Fpatience during this time."
OL,26,@tD@OOUyD@AOU|D@[O]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/5
