PN,43405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1782562704
OL,3,CTeenager charged with murder after
OL,4,Cbody found in search for missing girl
OL,6,FJenny Hopkins, a member of the Crown
OL,7,FProsecution Service, added: "It is
OL,8,Fextremely important that there should
OL,9,Fbe no reporting, commentary or sharing
OL,10,Fof information online which could in
OL,11,Fany way prejudice these proceedings."
OL,13,FGwent police are asking anyone with
OL,14,FCCTV footage or information which
OL,15,Fcould help the investigation to speak
OL,16,Fto officers, contact them via 101,
OL,17,Fquoting reference 2600194414, or
OL,18,Fonline.
OL,26,@oD@]OUsD@eO]
